{"word":"ἐπιτεχνάομαι","slug":"ἐπιτεχνάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιτεχνάομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ήσομαι</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐπιτεχνάομαι'><el>ἐπιτεχνάομαι</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to contrive for</i> a purpose or <i>to meet</i> an emergency, <i>to invent</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to contrive against</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}